=== Decision ===
  - If B (t-axis flat) recovers most → position-IDs at t>0 is the bug.
    Fix: pin latent t-axis = 0 in t2v._build_position_ids.
  - If C (LPE f-flat) recovers most → LPE at f>0 is the bug.
    Fix: investigate LPE table semantics for f>0 entries.
  - If D recovers but B,C partial → both contribute; need to fix both.
  - If none recovers → cause is elsewhere (mask, attention).
